        <p class="left"><b>storytelling:</b><br /> the art of using language, vocalization, and/or physical movement and gesture to reveal the elements and images of a story to a specific, live audience</p>
				<p class="right"><b>storybuilder:</b><br /> a tool that combines data, relationships, text, images, video, sound, and interactive media to tell stories that engage a live audience using the web</p>
